column2:
"You're here. I was waiting for you, <%me>.
I have something I wanted to ask you."
"I'd like to try fighting in a party of 4. Could you take me with you again?"
"Asuna and I make two, then there's you, so we just need one more..."
"Matoi, silly! It's about time all four of us got together, isn't it?"
"...Sure, that works. That's OK, right? I hate having to keep leaning on you like this. I'll make up for it next time, count on it."
